# apps/ai

Python FastAPI service for AI features. Standalone (not wired into Turborepo/Bun).

## Run

```bash
cd apps/ai
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...        # or: set -a; source ../../.env; set +a
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 3004
```

## Endpoints

- `GET /health` → `{"status": "ok"}`
- `POST /chat` `{"message": "..."}` → `{"reply": "..."}`

Model via `AI_MODEL` env (default `claude-opus-4-8`).
